Program: Outlook
Title: Tunisian Dr: 'Fighting Angel of Death'
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01nrh2g
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 7 Jan 2014
Dr Amen Allah Messadi talks to Marco Silva about treating young protesters in Tunisia who have set themselves on fire. Freda Kelly, who ran the The Beatles' fan club, gives the inside story of life with the Fab Four. Former 'Lost Boy' Jacob Mach who fled Sudan's civil war in the eighties and is now pursuing the American Dream. Bestselling author Neil Gaiman on his latest novel The Ocean at the End of the Lane. (Picture: Dr Amen Allah Messadi) Show less